BP EXPLORATION & PRODUCTION INC., et al., applicants,
v.
LAKE EUGENIE LAND & DEVELOPMENT, INC., et al. No. 13A1177. Supreme Court of the United States June 9, 2014. Case below, 744 F.3d 370 . Application to recall and stay the mandate of the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit presented to Justice SCALIA and by him referred to the Court denied.
